      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "label": "Recto - right margin",
          "value": "<p>Recto, Right Margin:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>She remained with him in the best possible situation. Nothing remains for me but the journey. I traveled to \u02bfAydha\u0304b, terrified and frightened by the ill-fated trip, but God</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>decreed my safe arrival. Now I intend to set out for India. May God, may He be praised, make the outcome good again! Everything that I have heard about what you (pl.) are undergoing and your circumstances</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>increased my distress over you.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>\u00a0</p>",
          "format": "text/html"
        }
